{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@UIEdgeInsets","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UIEdgeInsets"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"contentInset"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is equal to "},{"code":"UIEdgeInsetsZero","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", viewport"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"properties such as "},{"code":"centerCoordinate","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" assume a viewport that matches the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s frame. Otherwise, those properties are inset, excluding part of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"frame from the viewport. For instance, if the only the top edge is inset, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map center is effectively shifted downward."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the map view’s superview is an instance of "},{"code":"UIViewController","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" whose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property is "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the value of this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property may be overridden at any time."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The usage of "},{"code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" has been deprecated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use the map view’s property "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset"},{"type":"text","text":"instead."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"code":"-setContentInset:animated:completionHandler:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method instead."}]}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/contentInset"},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"contentInset","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)contentInset","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"contentInset"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1610"},"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"The distance from the edges of the map view’s frame to the edges of the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view’s logical viewport.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/contentinset"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre",